source.name: Front Yards In Bloom Nominations (2011) - Map View
source.description:
Shows all addresses that received nominations for the Front Yards in Bloom (FYinB) program in 2011. FYinB began in 1999 by the City of Edmonton, Edmonton Horticultural Society, and letter carriers. This shows all nominated addresses, starting in 2006, as well as top addresses from the beginning.
Any address can be nominated many times in one year.
